# Obsidian editor config (not project docs)
docs/.obsidian/

# Claude Code — machine-local + secret-bearing agent files only.
# CLAUDE.md (project orientation) and .claude/skills/ (the persona-review
# methodology) stay tracked on purpose — they help anyone who forks this repo.
# settings.local.json is per-machine convenience; .mcp.json can carry internal
# hostnames / knowledge-base collections. Those two don't belong in a public fork.
.claude/settings.local.json
.mcp.json
